    <summary>Switch to any running window instantly using configurable global hotkeys.</summary>
    <description>AppSwitcher is a Windows desktop application that lets you jump to any running window using a dedicated hotkey — no more Alt-Tabbing through a stack of windows.

Inspired by rCmd for macOS, AppSwitcher lets you assign a global hotkey to any application so you can reach it in one keystroke.

## Features

- Assign global hotkeys to switch directly to any running window
- Runs silently in the system tray
- Optional autostart with Windows
- Supports Windows 10 version 2004 (build 19041) or newer

## Notes

Requires .NET 8.0 or higher Desktop Runtime, automatically installed as a Chocolatey dependency.</description>
    <releaseNotes>https://github.com/ipatalas/app-switcher/releases</releaseNotes>
